Here is the fourth season of the Touch blu-ray box set. I used the [QTS](BD H264 960x720 AAC) files. I went through all the scripts after converting them to be used with blu-rays and made timing corrections, tried to catch grammar/typo mistakes, and tried to standardize various things. Then I watched them all and made more corrections. Hopefully I caught most of the problems.

And that's it for Touch TV. Enjoy
